            "title": "港股午後初段動力提升 一度升近200點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後動力提升，恒生指數早前最高衝上26123點，升195點。截至下午約1時40分，恒指報26103點，仍漲175點或0.68%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)升約4%；兩大藍籌國際金融股升勢亦擴大，友邦(01299)升約2.2%，滙控(00005)升約1.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特(09992)續於高位徘徊，暫升約8.6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15461326-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%8b%95%e5%8a%9b%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87-%e4%b8%80%e5%ba%a6%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%91200%e9%bb%9e",
